{
  "script_id": "steiner-chain",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.39,
      "size": 22176,
      "text": "给你一个大圆，里面再套一个小圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "能不能在这两个圆之间，塞进一圈小圆？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "每个小圆都贴着内外两圆，还挨着左右邻居。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.43,
      "size": 22896,
      "text": "这一串首尾相接的圆，就叫斯坦纳链。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "tangent",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "tangent-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/tangent-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "每个链圆同时内切外圆、外切内圆，被牢牢卡在环形区域里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "tangent",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "tangent-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/tangent-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "相邻两个链圆还要彼此外切，一环扣一环地排下去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "tangent",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "tangent-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/tangent-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "要正好绕一圈回到起点，圆的个数和两圆大小必须精确配合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "porism",
      "line_id": "por-1",
      "filename": "porism-por-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/porism-por-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.58,
      "size": 41328,
      "text": "同心情形下，闭合条件很漂亮：sin(π比n)等于半径差除以半径和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "porism",
      "line_id": "por-2",
      "filename": "porism-por-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/porism-por-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "斯坦纳发现了惊人的一点：只要链条能闭合一次，就能闭合无数次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "porism",
      "line_id": "por-3",
      "filename": "porism-por-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/porism-por-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "于是整条链可以自由地转动，起点放在哪里都照样严丝合缝。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "inversion",
      "line_id": "inv-1",
      "filename": "inversion-inv-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/inversion-inv-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "一般的两个圆并不同心，怎么造出它们之间的链呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "inversion",
      "line_id": "inv-2",
      "filename": "inversion-inv-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/inversion-inv-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "答案是圆反演：它把圆变成圆，还完好保留相切关系。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "inversion",
      "line_id": "inv-3",
      "filename": "inversion-inv-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/inversion-inv-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.41,
      "size": 38592,
      "text": "先在同心环里排好链，再一次反演，就得到任意两圆间的斯坦纳链。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "换一换链圆的个数，看内外圆的比例如何随之变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "让链条转起来，体会它无论怎么旋转都始终闭合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "斯坦纳链是夹在两圆之间、首尾相切的一圈圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.52,
      "size": 40320,
      "text": "闭合条件由半径决定，一旦闭合便能自由旋转，这就是斯坦纳定理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "steiner-chain",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/steiner-chain/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "圆反演把简单的同心链变成千姿百态的一般链，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.440000000000005,
